high_descs: Go to the left to pass the island and straight back to locate the coffee machine.
Open the cabinet below and pull out a cup. Shut the door.
Carry the cup and turn left to find the sink in the island.
Place the cup in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the cup from the sink.
Take the mug filled with water over to the coffee machine behind you, and to the right.
Place the mug under the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Fill up a mug with water and take to the coffee machine.

high_descs: Go left and turn left again to face the counter with the coffee pot on it.
Open the lower cabinet and take out the cup from the cupboard.
Go left and turn to face the sink.
Put the cup in the sink, turn the water on and then off and pick the cup up out of the sink.
Go left and then left again to face the coffee maker.
Put the cup under the coffee maker on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean cup under a coffee pot.

high_descs: Move to the bin, turn left, move to past the island, turn right, move to alongside the coffee maker, turn left, move to the counter.
Open the cupboard doors, pick up the mug, close the cupboard doors.
Turn left, move to the center of the basin on the left, turn left, move to the island.
Put the mug in the sink, turn on the faucet, fill the mug with water, turn off the faucet, pick up the mug.
Turn left, move to the coffee maker, turn left, move to the counter.
Place the mug in the coffee maker mug spot.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug of water in the coffee maker mug location.
